
*******Streamlit Add URL ********
https://conv-ai-assignment-2-grp-16-rag-finetune.streamlit.app

**** RAG API***
rag-server.py: Exposes API for RAG based question answering.
URL:   http://localhost:5000/rag/
Input: payload = {
                "query": user_input, "max_length": max_length
                 }

Note: RAG's FAST API is not used in the streamlit cloud. The version deployed on streamlit cloud is a 2-tier architecture where UI is directly
invoking the RAG backend and Finetuned model.

******* Fine Tune Model ******
Down load the model from huggingface.
URL: Anup77Jindal/gpt2-finetuned-model-v0.1


************* Streamlit Deployment *****************
Click on the Create App and Select the Git Repo
Git Repo: MTechAssignments/conversation_assignment_2
Python: 3.12.2
Dependencies
Class: streamlit_app_cloud
streamlit run src/ui/streamlit_app_cloud.py
